    "description": "{noformat}Feature: Catalog Management - Add New Book Title\n\n  Scenario: Successfully adding a new book title with valid details\n    Given I am logged in as a Librarian\n    And I am on the 'Catalog Management' page\n    When I input the Title 'Clean Code'\n    And I input the Author 'Robert C. Martin'\n    And I input the ISBN '978-0132350884'\n    And I click the 'Add New Book' button\n    Then the system should save the new book title 'Clean Code' to the catalog\n    And a success notification 'Book added successfully' should be displayed\n    And the 'Catalog Management' page should display the new book title 'Clean Code'\n\n  Scenario: Attempting to add a book title with a missing required field (e.g., Title)\n    Given I am logged in as a Librarian\n    And I am on the 'Catalog Management' page\n    When I input the Author 'Robert C. Martin'\n    And I input the ISBN '978-0132350884'\n    And I leave the Title field empty\n    And I click the 'Add New Book' button\n    Then an error message 'Title is a required field' should be displayed\n    And the book title should not be saved to the catalog\n\n  Scenario: Attempting to add a book title with a duplicate ISBN\n    Given I am logged in as a Librarian\n    And I am on the 'Catalog Management' page\n    And a book with ISBN '978-0132350884' already exists in the catalog\n    When I input the Title 'Another Book'\n    And I input the Author 'Some Author'\n    And I input the ISBN '978-0132350884'\n    And I click the 'Add New Book' button\n    Then an error message 'A book with this ISBN already exists' should be displayed\n    And the book title 'Another Book' should not be saved to the catalog\n\n  Scenario: Attempting to add a book title with an invalid ISBN format\n    Given I am logged in as a Librarian\n    And I am on the 'Catalog Management' page\n    When I input the Title 'Invalid ISBN Book'\n    And I input the Author 'Test Author'\n    And I input the ISBN 'INVALID-ISBN'\n    And I click the 'Add New Book' button\n    Then an error message 'Invalid ISBN format' should be displayed\n    And the book title 'Invalid ISBN Book' should not be saved to the catalog\n\n  Scenario: Cancelling the addition of a new book title\n    Given I am logged in as a Librarian\n    And I am on the 'Catalog Management' page\n    When I input the Title 'Temporary Book'\n    And I input the Author 'Temp Author'\n    And I input the ISBN '123-4567890123'\n    And I click the 'Cancel' button\n    Then the system should discard the entered book details\n    And the 'Catalog Management' page should not display the book title 'Temporary Book'{noformat}",
